<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这情景糟透了。到处都有人在吵架打架。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些人甚至在大哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨和詹金斯夫人看都不看对方一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们没有什么好的话要说吗？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女人都固执地摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比和赛伊陷入了另一场争论里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的行为就像个小孩子。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太喜欢发号施令了。”鲍比回击说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，简在和基弗先生说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最欢的糖果是红樱桃的。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得你吃太多糖了。”店主基弗先生说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我吃的糖没有鲍比多。”她大声回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以他才这么胖。”潘瑟忍不下去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就没人能说点儿好听的话吗？”她大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有那么一秒钟，人们都停止了说话。他们都瞪着潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的天，你的声音真的是太大了！”詹金斯夫人讨厌地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真的非常粗鲁。”一个男人皱着眉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟真想钻到地缝里去。一切都是她的错。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘特。”兰姆轻轻地叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出了胖胖的小胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟把他从玛莎阿姨那里抱了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆咯咯笑着。潘瑟看着兰姆的眼睛。她看了很久。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没有什么不好的，兰姆。”她温柔地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看看四周，补充说：“我希望我们都能像你一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟仔细想了想她刚才说的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只想着人们好的地方。”她告诉兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这让她有了一个主意。“玛莎阿姨。”她突然说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，孩子？”玛莎阿姨尖声问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您对我们这么好。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她认真的思考了自己真正的感受。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们知道照顾我们很不容易。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她继续说，“所以我们很珍惜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，你们这些孩子有时很烦人。”玛莎阿姨真心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但至少你们很懂礼貌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟走向了赛伊和鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们就没有什么好话能说吗？”她问自己的兄弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比固执地抱着胳膊摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊将脑袋转到一边，对鲍比视而不见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看你们自己的内心。”潘瑟对自己的兄弟们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我肯定你们会找到好的一面，而不仅仅是不好的一面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看看彼此。鲍比对着赛伊吐了吐舌头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟大声叹了口气，然后说：“人们应该说出自己内心的想法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但如果我们心里想的只有美好的事情呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇上的一些居民停止了争吵去听潘瑟说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真心表达自己并不意味着要成为被人讨厌的人。”她继续说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看了看赛伊。赛伊迅速对他一笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有时候，语言并不是必须的。”潘瑟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但如果你必须说点什么，你可以说一些好听的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，虽然赛伊欺负我，”鲍比说，“但有时候他很酷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虽然鲍比是个胖子，”简咯咯笑道，“但他很有意思。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比脸红了。“我不胖！”他嚷到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊很快打断了他弟弟的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘瑟说得对。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以用友好的方式做到诚实。对吧，简？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简依然在咯咯笑，但她点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆给了潘瑟一个大大的拥抱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她紧紧地抱住了兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，玛莎阿姨从潘瑟那里把兰姆接了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，孩子们！”她说，“我们回家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从詹金斯夫人身边走过的时候，她停下来笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>詹金斯夫人也笑了。其他人也都停止了争吵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的人又重新有了笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们到家的时候，孩子们坐在了外面的门廊里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳依然在天上闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们觉得这个愿望怎样才能结束？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>366318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像潘瑟许愿的那样啊。”赛伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>366319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>370058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会说出我们心里想的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>370059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>375697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们只能想好的想法啊。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>375698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>381853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“至少我们会这样去努力。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>381854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>386228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他依然为简说他胖生着气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>386229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>390710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们紧紧地坐在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>390711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>397794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有你们在我身边真是太幸运了。”潘瑟对她的兄弟姐妹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>397795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>402247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这才是我的心里话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>